t.com/chromecast-with-google-tv-hd-1080p-hdr-remote-130016962.html">Chromecast with Google TV (HD)</a>和 50 美元的 4K 型号。</p><p>如果您是<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2018-07-24-google-chromecast-at-five.html">忠实的第一代 Chromecast 用户</a>，现在唯一要做的就是确保它已全面升级并希望一切顺利。</p>本文最初出现在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/google-has-officially-stopped-supporting-the-first-gen-chromecast-095205330.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/google-has-officially-stopped-supporting-the-first-gen-chromecast-095205330.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> eb93a0cd-a114-42e8-a1bd-afe89f47e025</guid><dc:creator> Sarah Fielding</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher> Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Wed, 31 May 2023 09:52:05 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1685526725</ingested><modified> 2023-05-31T09:52:11+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Information Technology]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Sarah Fielding]]></category><media:content height="540" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/dims-shared/dims3/GLOB/crop/960x540+0+0/resize/960x540!/format/jpg/quality/85/https://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/midas/dc15caa91cfcc94bf548b6670dcba148/201267679/Chromecast__DSC4027.jpg" width="960"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="540" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/dims-shared/dims3/GLOB/crop/960x540+0+0/resize/960x540!/format/jpg/quality/85/https://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/midas/dc15ca